WEBVTT

01:30.890 --> 01:35.000
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.880 --> 01:39.460
[2020]

01:43.430 --> 01:45.360
Having a birthday on New Year's Day

01:45.430 --> 01:46.400
means you clash with

01:46.400 --> 01:48.259
the entire world's celebration.

01:48.560 --> 01:49.000
It means

01:49.000 --> 01:51.840
you're always forgotten
amidst the revelry.

01:52.640 --> 01:54.840
Everyone looks forward to the new year,

01:55.350 --> 01:56.479
and no one cares

01:57.430 --> 01:59.000
that you're a year older.

02:06.420 --> 02:07.350
Happy Birthday,

02:07.840 --> 02:08.600
Xia Xiaolan.

02:11.500 --> 02:14.470
[Episode 17: Happy Birthday to You]

02:16.910 --> 02:17.640
Will this do?

02:17.960 --> 02:18.680
Yes.

02:19.430 --> 02:20.120
That's all.

02:20.240 --> 02:20.710
Okay.

02:20.910 --> 02:21.750
Please wait a moment.

02:21.750 --> 02:22.680
Okay, thank you.

02:23.910 --> 02:24.590
Earlier,

02:24.710 --> 02:25.520
I told your mom

02:25.630 --> 02:27.190
that we should come try this restaurant

02:27.190 --> 02:29.120
after I got back from my business trip.

02:29.120 --> 02:30.579
I really didn't expect you

02:30.710 --> 02:32.190
to be free today.

02:33.280 --> 02:34.310
Will your clothing store

02:34.310 --> 02:35.400
be okay

02:35.630 --> 02:36.690
without you there?

02:37.240 --> 02:39.440
Looks like he doesn't want me to be here.

02:40.440 --> 02:41.810
A boss needs to trust

02:41.840 --> 02:42.700
her employees.

02:43.150 --> 02:44.140
Mr. Tang, you usually

02:44.140 --> 02:45.470
have a lot on your plate.

02:45.710 --> 02:46.840
Focusing on the big picture
and not sweating the small stuff—

02:46.840 --> 02:48.430
you know that better than I do.

02:48.430 --> 02:49.430
Nice restaurant.

02:49.430 --> 02:50.000
Yes.

02:51.750 --> 02:53.590
Let's get a table first.

02:54.030 --> 02:54.960
Tang?

02:56.430 --> 02:57.560
What a coincidence.

02:58.590 --> 02:59.150
Hello.

03:01.670 --> 03:03.710
This must be Liu Fen, right?

03:05.030 --> 03:05.520
Hello.

03:06.080 --> 03:07.280
Hello, I am.

03:08.560 --> 03:10.020
When eating Western food,

03:10.200 --> 03:12.260
do you know which hand holds the knife

03:12.320 --> 03:13.720
and which holds the fork?

03:14.710 --> 03:15.310
I forgot.

03:15.750 --> 03:16.930
Don't treat it
like when you were in the countryside,

03:16.930 --> 03:18.420
chopping pig feed with a blade.

03:18.420 --> 03:19.620
If you use them wrong,

03:19.680 --> 03:21.560
you'll embarrass yourself
in front of the foreign guests.

03:21.560 --> 03:23.630
It's been so long
since the Reform and Opening-Up,

03:23.630 --> 03:24.960
yet some people

03:25.240 --> 03:27.360
still like to pretend to be foreigners

03:27.360 --> 03:28.960
and worship foreign things.

03:29.520 --> 03:31.720
Does it matter if we use a knife and fork?

03:31.870 --> 03:33.000
This is Shengcheng.

03:33.360 --> 03:34.630
I'm paying to eat.

03:35.140 --> 03:36.240
If I use a knife and fork,

03:36.240 --> 03:38.430
it's to respect their culinary culture.

03:38.430 --> 03:39.590
If I don't want to,

03:39.780 --> 03:40.740
shouldn't they

03:40.910 --> 03:41.630
just give me

03:41.630 --> 03:42.840
a pair of chopsticks?

03:43.430 --> 03:44.560
Right, Mr. Tang?

03:45.360 --> 03:45.890
Xiaolan,

03:46.000 --> 03:48.000
I think what you said is really good.

03:48.520 --> 03:49.150
Actually,

03:49.520 --> 03:50.250
where you eat

03:50.590 --> 03:51.630
and what utensils you use

03:51.630 --> 03:53.030
are not important at all.

03:53.960 --> 03:54.820
What matters is

04:03.680 --> 04:05.010
who you are eating with.

04:27.720 --> 04:28.560
Mr. Tang,

04:29.260 --> 04:31.180
we don't know

04:31.360 --> 04:32.510
that lady just now.

04:33.000 --> 04:34.950
But she knew my mom's name.

04:35.830 --> 04:37.600
Shouldn't you explain?

04:44.720 --> 04:45.720
She is my ex-wife.

04:47.070 --> 04:48.000
Her name is Ji Ya.

04:48.040 --> 04:49.640
She studied fashion design.

04:49.800 --> 04:51.460
She just came back from the US.

04:52.630 --> 04:53.720
This is probably the second time

04:53.720 --> 04:55.720
I've seen her here.

04:57.120 --> 04:58.390
The first time

04:58.600 --> 04:59.750
was two weeks ago.

05:00.240 --> 05:02.240
She came to my office looking for me.

05:02.750 --> 05:03.600
At that time,

05:04.650 --> 05:05.480
she talked a lot about

05:05.480 --> 05:06.360
the past.

05:07.190 --> 05:08.790
I understood what she meant,

05:09.360 --> 05:09.920
but I

05:09.920 --> 05:11.520
made it very clear to her then

05:11.870 --> 05:12.730
that right now,

05:13.720 --> 05:15.580
there is someone I want to be with,

05:16.310 --> 05:17.110
someone I want

05:17.830 --> 05:19.630
to spend the rest of my life with.

05:26.040 --> 05:26.560
Mom.

05:27.630 --> 05:28.870
That...

05:30.310 --> 05:31.430
Ms. Ji just now—

05:32.270 --> 05:33.670
judging by her reaction,

05:34.430 --> 05:36.240
what Mr. Tang said must be true.

05:45.750 --> 05:46.610
Here, Xiaolan.

05:53.530 --> 05:54.000
Thank you.

05:54.000 --> 05:54.930
You're welcome.

05:58.920 --> 05:59.520
Thank you.

06:02.430 --> 06:03.090
Mayor Tang,

06:03.310 --> 06:04.240
here are the chopsticks you asked for.

06:04.240 --> 06:05.640
-Okay.
-Enjoy your meal.

06:09.390 --> 06:10.870
If you don't like
using the knife and fork,

06:10.870 --> 06:12.530
I'll use chopsticks with you.

06:13.720 --> 06:14.320
It's fine.

06:15.190 --> 06:15.800
No need.

06:37.630 --> 06:38.950
Why are you two staring at me?

06:38.950 --> 06:40.210
Why aren't you eating?

06:40.950 --> 06:41.510
Mom,

06:42.360 --> 06:43.750
I only taught you once.

06:44.800 --> 06:46.860
I didn't expect you to be so good at it.

06:47.360 --> 06:49.290
I just felt I might need it someday.

06:49.360 --> 06:51.290
I didn't expect to actually use it.

06:52.430 --> 06:53.690
I practiced secretly.

06:54.750 --> 06:56.409
I didn't embarrass you, did I?

06:57.690 --> 06:58.280
Your mom

06:58.310 --> 06:59.720
uses them better than I do.

06:59.720 --> 07:01.680
I've forgotten it should be

07:01.680 --> 07:02.450
knife in the left hand
and fork in the right

07:02.450 --> 07:03.780
or the other way around.

07:06.390 --> 07:06.870
So,

07:07.310 --> 07:08.710
that's your ex-husband?

07:09.360 --> 07:11.680
Seems like he's in a new relationship.

07:12.360 --> 07:13.560
But this is good news.

07:13.950 --> 07:16.010
Looks like I've got a good chance now.

07:17.920 --> 07:18.390
George,

07:18.870 --> 07:21.270
we are just business partners and friends.

07:22.630 --> 07:25.360
I don't really want any other factors

07:25.430 --> 07:27.160
affecting our cooperation.

07:28.800 --> 07:29.680
It's okay.

07:30.270 --> 07:31.330
It's not a big deal.

07:32.310 --> 07:33.190
Have a piece of this.

07:33.190 --> 07:33.790
Thank you.

07:34.240 --> 07:35.190
Xiaolan, have a piece of this.

07:35.190 --> 07:36.320
Thank you, Mr. Tang.

07:39.120 --> 07:39.630
Okay.

07:40.070 --> 07:40.930
I'm not hungry.

07:41.270 --> 07:41.950
I will go.

07:47.830 --> 07:48.760
Let's just eat.

07:49.430 --> 07:50.760
Try this mushroom soup.

07:53.270 --> 07:53.830
Goodbye.

07:54.310 --> 07:54.840
Bye-bye.

07:55.720 --> 07:56.320
Excuse me.

07:56.560 --> 07:57.820
I'm gonna get the bill.

08:02.000 --> 08:03.310
This is such a waste.

08:04.160 --> 08:06.120
How about I bring them over?

08:08.310 --> 08:08.830
Here.

08:14.270 --> 08:15.330
Alright, this way.

08:15.630 --> 08:16.230
Thank you.

08:16.560 --> 08:17.360
You're welcome, Mr. Tang.

08:17.360 --> 08:17.870
Bye.

08:18.390 --> 08:19.120
Please come again.

08:19.120 --> 08:20.050
Okay, thank you.

08:22.920 --> 08:23.950
It's still early.

08:24.070 --> 08:25.190
And we're quite full.

08:25.190 --> 08:26.430
How about we take a walk

08:26.430 --> 08:27.070
to digest?

08:27.480 --> 08:28.000
Sure.

08:28.270 --> 08:28.800
Xiaolan,

08:28.950 --> 08:30.280
if you have things to do,

08:30.390 --> 08:31.320
you can go ahead.

08:31.870 --> 08:32.750
Considering how well

08:32.750 --> 08:34.350
you dealt with Jiya just now,

08:34.720 --> 08:35.960
I'll let you off the hook.

08:35.960 --> 08:36.390
Right.

08:36.630 --> 08:37.600
I happen to be meeting Zhenzhu

08:37.600 --> 08:38.840
to discuss something.

08:38.840 --> 08:40.020
Don't stay out too late.

08:40.020 --> 08:40.820
Go home early.

08:41.120 --> 08:41.600
Okay.

08:42.240 --> 08:42.789
Bye-bye.

08:47.630 --> 08:48.240
Let's go.

08:50.910 --> 08:52.200
My behavior today

08:52.320 --> 08:53.780
was actually very abrupt.

08:54.320 --> 08:55.780
I want to apologize to you.

08:55.790 --> 08:56.390
I'm sorry.

08:57.080 --> 08:58.280
I hope you don't mind.

08:59.390 --> 09:00.790
There's nothing to mind.

09:02.000 --> 09:04.330
It's just that after seeing your ex-wife,

09:04.510 --> 09:05.910
I feel even more strongly

09:06.720 --> 09:08.920
that we aren't suitable for each other.

09:09.320 --> 09:10.000
I don't know

09:10.000 --> 09:11.440
what you see in me.

09:12.960 --> 09:14.510
The gap between us is so big.

09:15.320 --> 09:17.050
We can't build a life together.

09:18.870 --> 09:19.670
If...

09:20.270 --> 09:21.720
I appear by your side,

09:22.360 --> 09:23.760
people will laugh at you.

09:25.840 --> 09:27.040
I don't think there is

09:27.200 --> 09:28.260
any gap between us.

09:29.320 --> 09:31.120
And you said people would laugh at me.

09:31.120 --> 09:32.920
That's a problem for me to solve.

09:33.030 --> 09:34.960
You must not put pressure on yourself

09:34.960 --> 09:35.890
because of this.

09:37.720 --> 09:38.650
Comrade Liu Fen,

09:39.270 --> 09:40.200
I don't mean to

09:40.320 --> 09:42.050
cling to you in a malicious way.

09:42.120 --> 09:43.080
I just feel that

09:43.790 --> 09:44.990
you don't dislike me.

09:46.670 --> 09:48.150
If I may be so bold,

09:49.480 --> 09:51.000
perhaps you have at least

09:51.870 --> 09:53.670
a little bit of affection for me.

09:55.080 --> 09:56.910
So let's just let nature take its course

09:56.910 --> 09:57.970
and date normally.

09:59.360 --> 10:00.090
Is that okay?

10:22.720 --> 10:24.320
I can't answer you right now.

10:26.150 --> 10:27.270
Can you wait for me?

10:30.840 --> 10:32.000
Whatever you want to do,

10:32.000 --> 10:33.150
or however you want to do it,

10:33.150 --> 10:34.610
I support you 100 percent.

10:36.840 --> 10:37.900
Actually, you see.

10:38.000 --> 10:38.870
The two of us

10:39.320 --> 10:40.790
are already standing together now.

10:40.790 --> 10:42.720
And we are face-to-face like this.

10:42.960 --> 10:44.620
There's no need for me to wait.

10:45.240 --> 10:46.240
I'll give you time

10:46.320 --> 10:47.580
to think this through.

10:47.980 --> 10:49.440
Let's just date normally.

10:56.120 --> 10:56.750
Watch out.

10:58.490 --> 10:59.350
Let me help you.

10:59.550 --> 11:00.440
-Okay.
-The stairs are right ahead.

11:00.440 --> 11:01.600
Thank you. Thank you.

11:01.600 --> 11:02.550
It's okay.

11:02.570 --> 11:03.500
You're welcome.

11:04.320 --> 11:04.980
Be careful.

11:05.000 --> 11:05.390
Okay.

11:10.000 --> 11:10.750
Xia!

11:12.390 --> 11:13.150
Xia!

11:14.360 --> 11:14.840
Xia!

11:14.910 --> 11:15.440
Coming.

11:15.440 --> 11:17.120
What's the matter? Why the rush?

11:17.120 --> 11:17.980
Let me tell you.

11:18.120 --> 11:18.910
I got it.

11:19.320 --> 11:20.790
It's also a women's clothing store

11:20.790 --> 11:22.150
across the street.

11:22.390 --> 11:23.440
The owner is a designer

11:23.440 --> 11:24.320
back from the US.

11:24.320 --> 11:25.390
From the US?

11:25.790 --> 11:26.550
A foreigner?

11:26.840 --> 11:27.390
No.

11:27.630 --> 11:29.200
She lived in the US for years.

11:29.200 --> 11:31.130
She just came back. She's Chinese.

11:31.550 --> 11:32.320
Her name...

11:33.600 --> 11:34.660
She's surnamed Ji.

11:36.440 --> 11:37.320
Ji?

11:37.750 --> 11:38.870
Back from the US?

11:39.630 --> 11:40.560
Her name is Ji Ya.

11:40.580 --> 11:42.180
She studied fashion design.

11:42.360 --> 11:44.020
She just came back from the US.

11:44.670 --> 11:46.150
It can't be that coincidental, can it?

11:46.150 --> 11:47.410
Alright, case solved.

11:47.750 --> 11:48.270
Mom,

11:48.510 --> 11:49.390
you've run into

11:49.390 --> 11:50.790
a jealous psycho.

11:51.800 --> 11:52.730
What do you mean?

11:53.200 --> 11:54.790
Mom and I met Mr. Tang's ex-wife

11:54.790 --> 11:56.480
at a restaurant before.

11:56.600 --> 11:57.390
She is that designer

11:57.390 --> 11:58.480
back from the US.

11:58.500 --> 11:59.430
Her name is Ji Ya.

12:00.120 --> 12:01.870
I reckon

12:02.390 --> 12:04.050
she wants to remarry Mr. Tang.

12:04.240 --> 12:04.720
But since

12:04.720 --> 12:05.870
Mr. Tang is pursuing you,

12:05.870 --> 12:06.800
he rejected her.

12:07.080 --> 12:08.600
She's now angry out of humiliation

12:08.600 --> 12:09.440
and wants to compete with you

12:09.440 --> 12:10.360
in business.

12:11.720 --> 12:12.720
She's just a

12:12.720 --> 12:15.120
brainless fake foreigner.

12:15.720 --> 12:16.630
But

12:17.230 --> 12:18.960
she stayed in the US for a while.

12:19.270 --> 12:20.800
She must be sophisticated.

12:23.510 --> 12:24.370
Are you scared?

12:25.240 --> 12:25.960
I...

12:30.750 --> 12:31.610
I'm not scared.

12:31.840 --> 12:33.000
That's the spirit.

12:35.120 --> 12:35.670
Chen.

12:36.030 --> 12:36.870
What about you?

12:36.870 --> 12:38.070
Why would I be scared?

12:38.600 --> 12:39.130
Alright.

12:39.480 --> 12:40.120
Then Chen,

12:40.370 --> 12:41.880
use all your connections.

12:41.910 --> 12:43.290
I want all information on Ji Ya

12:43.290 --> 12:44.620
and her previous works.

12:44.670 --> 12:46.030
After all, know the enemy and yourself,

12:46.030 --> 12:47.390
and you'll never be defeated.

12:47.390 --> 12:47.960
Okay!

12:48.270 --> 12:49.270
Let's go. I'll go with you.

12:49.270 --> 12:49.800
Let's go.

12:50.030 --> 12:50.890
Mom, we're off.

12:59.510 --> 13:00.510
What do you think?

13:00.670 --> 13:02.670
From a design perspective,

13:03.030 --> 13:04.360
she is indeed talented.

13:04.440 --> 13:05.720
The tailoring is smooth,

13:05.720 --> 13:07.240
and some Western elements

13:07.320 --> 13:08.650
are used very cleverly.

13:09.030 --> 13:10.490
Are you really not scared?

13:12.670 --> 13:14.150
In terms of design alone,

13:14.320 --> 13:15.870
it's hard to say who's better.

13:15.870 --> 13:17.240
But running a brand

13:17.240 --> 13:18.480
isn't just about design.

13:18.480 --> 13:19.840
If you only have design,

13:20.150 --> 13:21.080
you won't go far.

13:21.270 --> 13:22.030
Why should I be scared?

13:22.030 --> 13:22.550
I'm not.

13:23.360 --> 13:23.960
Good.

13:24.510 --> 13:25.240
Since you're not scared,

13:25.240 --> 13:27.040
the branch will open as planned.

13:27.320 --> 13:27.870
Okay.

13:28.320 --> 13:29.580
Mr. Chen, don't worry.

13:29.840 --> 13:31.150
We can discuss the contract details later.

13:31.150 --> 13:31.510
Okay.

13:31.870 --> 13:32.840
If you need

13:32.840 --> 13:34.030
a large quantity of these fabrics,

13:34.030 --> 13:35.320
I can offer you a discount.

13:35.320 --> 13:35.960
Okay.

13:35.960 --> 13:36.550
Rest assured.

13:36.550 --> 13:37.440
No problem.

13:37.790 --> 13:39.030
Mr. Huang, you have a phone call.

13:39.030 --> 13:40.030
Okay. Excuse me.

13:42.360 --> 13:42.960
This is he.

13:43.630 --> 13:45.510
Okay, okay.

13:47.550 --> 13:48.080
Mr. Chen,

13:48.200 --> 13:48.840
I'm sorry.

13:49.120 --> 13:49.910
This batch of goods

13:49.910 --> 13:50.910
might be delayed.

13:51.180 --> 13:52.240
Someone offered a higher price

13:52.240 --> 13:53.500
and wants it urgently.

13:56.000 --> 13:57.120
Come on, Mr. Huang...

13:57.120 --> 13:57.920
Stop chasing.

13:59.080 --> 14:01.140
Looks like Ms. Ji Ya has made her move.

14:05.110 --> 14:06.810
[Luna]

14:09.270 --> 14:09.840
Xia.

14:10.390 --> 14:11.480
What do these

14:11.600 --> 14:12.720
English words mean?

14:12.720 --> 14:13.390
Elegance.

14:13.600 --> 14:14.400
It means "Ya."

14:14.750 --> 14:15.600
I didn't think

14:15.670 --> 14:17.470
she would name it after herself.

14:18.550 --> 14:19.550
So narcissistic.

14:19.750 --> 14:20.910
This name

14:20.910 --> 14:21.840
is such a mouthful.

14:21.840 --> 14:23.840
It would be a miracle if it takes off.

14:23.840 --> 14:24.720
Chen,

14:24.790 --> 14:25.990
you really are sharp.

14:26.320 --> 14:27.350
That makes sense.

14:35.750 --> 14:37.550
-Taste it. It's sweet.
-Come on.

14:37.870 --> 14:39.030
Today's ingredients

14:39.030 --> 14:40.030
are fresh off the boat.

14:40.030 --> 14:40.790
They are incredibly fresh.

14:40.790 --> 14:41.360
Try them.

14:41.750 --> 14:42.550
Thanks, San.

14:42.600 --> 14:43.390
Thanks, San.

14:43.480 --> 14:44.030
Thanks, San.

14:44.030 --> 14:44.960
You're welcome.

14:46.150 --> 14:47.750
You see, every time you come,

14:47.750 --> 14:48.720
you're always together.

14:48.720 --> 14:49.860
That's really enviable.

14:49.860 --> 14:50.930
Of course.

14:50.960 --> 14:52.200
We are family.

14:52.270 --> 14:53.550
We must come together.

14:53.600 --> 14:54.130
Alright.

14:54.200 --> 14:55.240
You guys enjoy the food.

14:55.240 --> 14:56.080
Call me if you need anything.

14:56.080 --> 14:56.630
Okay.

14:56.870 --> 14:57.550
Eat up.

15:00.910 --> 15:02.550
Well, this Ji Ya has

15:02.630 --> 15:04.360
capital from the US backing her.

15:04.360 --> 15:05.510
What should we do?

15:05.690 --> 15:06.430
Do you want me to get

15:06.430 --> 15:08.160
a few of my seniors and juniors?

15:09.080 --> 15:09.750
Sis Bai,

15:10.200 --> 15:11.840
there's a lawyer sitting right here.

15:11.840 --> 15:12.970
What are you saying?

15:13.150 --> 15:14.350
Just to spar a little.

15:14.960 --> 15:15.550
This Ji Ya—

15:15.550 --> 15:17.240
although she's not very bright,

15:17.240 --> 15:19.150
the methods she's currently using

15:19.150 --> 15:20.870
count as fair competition.

15:21.200 --> 15:21.930
Don't worry.

15:22.000 --> 15:23.030
We won't fight her head-on.

15:23.030 --> 15:24.030
I have other ways.

15:24.320 --> 15:24.790
Yes.

15:25.480 --> 15:27.390
There's nothing you can't handle.

15:27.390 --> 15:28.200
Chen,

15:28.550 --> 15:30.750
have you found a candidate

15:30.870 --> 15:32.130
for the store manager?

15:32.770 --> 15:34.090
In Longcheng,

15:34.120 --> 15:35.580
I plan to promote Xiaohui.

15:37.000 --> 15:38.000
As for Shengcheng,

15:38.000 --> 15:39.720
I think we should choose You Li.

15:39.720 --> 15:41.830
She's eager to learn and hardworking.

15:41.830 --> 15:43.240
Let her get some experience first.

15:43.240 --> 15:44.510
In the future, I want to

15:44.510 --> 15:45.720
groom her to be

15:45.720 --> 15:47.050
my personal assistant.

15:47.480 --> 15:48.120
Xiaolan,

15:48.550 --> 15:49.510
about this You Li...

15:49.510 --> 15:50.490
there's something

15:50.490 --> 15:52.020
I'm not sure if I should say.

15:53.200 --> 15:53.840
Actually,

15:54.030 --> 15:55.430
I knew You Li from before.

16:02.360 --> 16:03.120
Thank you.

16:04.630 --> 16:05.550
Kang Wei?

16:06.200 --> 16:08.150
Why are you fetching hot water yourself?

16:08.150 --> 16:09.240
Why didn't you call the nurse?

16:09.240 --> 16:09.840
No need.

16:09.840 --> 16:10.510
Where is Mrs. Xie?

16:10.510 --> 16:11.200
She's here.

16:11.200 --> 16:12.080
I'll do it myself.

16:12.080 --> 16:12.600
It's fine. It's fine.

16:12.600 --> 16:13.120
I'll carry them.

16:13.120 --> 16:14.000
No, really, it's fine.

16:14.000 --> 16:14.720
Your arm is injured.

16:14.720 --> 16:15.840
-Wei?
-I can...

16:15.910 --> 16:16.570
Your arm...

16:16.670 --> 16:18.000
Sis Bai, Sis Bai, hurry.

16:18.600 --> 16:19.510
Who is this?

16:20.200 --> 16:20.960
This is...

16:21.120 --> 16:22.030
You Li.

16:24.440 --> 16:25.270
How could you let her...

16:25.270 --> 16:26.030
It's fine. I'll do it.

16:26.030 --> 16:26.390
Let me do it.

16:26.390 --> 16:27.600
Give them to him. Come on.

16:27.600 --> 16:28.480
Give them all to me.

16:28.480 --> 16:29.410
Hold them tight.

16:29.480 --> 16:29.910
Sis,

16:29.910 --> 16:31.790
g-give me a hand, will you?

16:33.440 --> 16:34.970
Why don't you give me a hand?

16:36.030 --> 16:37.240
Just help me a bit.

16:37.240 --> 16:38.380
Get on. I'll carry you on my back.

16:38.380 --> 16:39.510
I'm afraid you don't have that strength.

16:39.510 --> 16:41.000
Just hold me.

16:41.080 --> 16:41.810
Just hold me.

16:42.210 --> 16:44.000
It hurts! Be gentle!

16:45.790 --> 16:47.120
You're so fussy.

16:47.150 --> 16:47.720
I...

16:47.750 --> 16:48.080
Let's go!

16:48.080 --> 16:49.480
So that's what happened?

16:49.720 --> 16:51.320
I thought she was sincere.

16:51.320 --> 16:52.260
I didn't expect she was just...

16:52.260 --> 16:53.520
trying to curry favor.

16:54.150 --> 16:55.200
I asked Sis Bai

16:55.200 --> 16:56.510
to pretend to be my girlfriend.

16:56.510 --> 16:58.000
That was how I made her give up.

16:58.000 --> 16:59.370
And it wasn't the first time.

16:59.370 --> 17:00.200
She came to my ward

17:00.200 --> 17:01.550
and visited me several times.

17:01.550 --> 17:03.150
How could I not overthink it?

17:03.510 --> 17:04.470
You know, back then,

17:04.470 --> 17:05.119
I was lying there

17:05.119 --> 17:06.069
like an invalid.

17:06.109 --> 17:07.109
She must have been after

17:07.109 --> 17:08.170
my family's money.

17:08.510 --> 17:09.589
I couldn't possibly

17:09.589 --> 17:11.440
believe she liked me for myself.

17:11.880 --> 17:13.339
I don't believe it either.

17:13.400 --> 17:16.069
Unless she, like... Ji Ya,

17:16.099 --> 17:17.140
is out of her mind.

17:18.680 --> 17:19.310
Alright.

17:19.550 --> 17:21.280
I'll observe a bit longer then.

17:21.310 --> 17:22.790
But if You Li really was

17:22.790 --> 17:24.270
a gold digger like you described,

17:24.270 --> 17:25.030
she wouldn't have backed off

17:25.030 --> 17:27.030
just because you have a girlfriend.

17:36.160 --> 17:37.240
Here, give it to me.

17:38.880 --> 17:39.550
Hello.

17:39.640 --> 17:40.160
Please.

17:49.750 --> 17:51.400
Hello. Welcome to Luna.

17:52.640 --> 17:54.100
What would you like to see?

17:54.200 --> 17:55.440
Do you have any new shoes?

17:55.440 --> 17:55.960
Yes.

17:56.010 --> 17:57.250
We have new arrivals.

18:01.000 --> 18:02.070
This blue pair

18:02.070 --> 18:02.550
is one of our

18:02.550 --> 18:03.790
classics.

18:03.920 --> 18:05.450
You can try it on if you like.

18:05.880 --> 18:06.750
And there's...

18:06.920 --> 18:07.640
this one.

18:08.000 --> 18:09.170
This one is also...

18:09.210 --> 18:10.200
easy to match with different outfits.

18:10.200 --> 18:11.000
Gathering intelligence?

18:11.000 --> 18:12.200
It has many small diamonds on it.

18:12.200 --> 18:12.930
You're here.

18:15.070 --> 18:16.160
Look, this You Li

18:16.550 --> 18:18.720
is different from what Kang Wei described.

18:18.720 --> 18:20.400
Either she's very scheming

18:20.400 --> 18:21.400
and hides it well,

18:21.790 --> 18:22.880
or she has

18:23.240 --> 18:24.040
other reasons

18:24.110 --> 18:25.240
for approaching Kang Wei.

18:25.240 --> 18:27.160
This one features embroidery.

18:28.480 --> 18:29.080
Oh, right.

18:32.150 --> 18:33.000
Shop lease,

18:33.310 --> 18:34.440
supplier contract,

18:34.640 --> 18:35.850
and transport contract.

18:35.850 --> 18:38.110
[Contract for Transportation
of Clothing Fabrics]

18:36.440 --> 18:37.310
Ji Ya is so

18:37.400 --> 18:38.550
focused on you

18:38.830 --> 18:39.640
that she didn't notice

18:39.640 --> 18:40.480
we've already split up

18:40.480 --> 18:41.720
and signed the contracts.

18:41.720 --> 18:44.200
We can tell Uncle
to start the renovation now.

18:44.200 --> 18:46.200
Dealing with Ji Ya is a piece of cake.

18:46.680 --> 18:49.010
Who doesn't have a few disguises out here?

18:52.400 --> 18:53.310
Come on in.

18:53.720 --> 18:54.270
Look.

18:54.590 --> 18:55.850
It's so big and spacious.

18:55.850 --> 18:56.840
[Jingyi Fabric Garment Factory–
Long-Term Recruitment]

18:56.510 --> 18:58.550
Let's use a diversion tactic

18:58.750 --> 19:00.210
and not fight her head-on.

19:00.590 --> 19:01.590
I'll take the heat

19:01.590 --> 19:02.480
in the open,

19:02.720 --> 19:03.310
and you guys handle

19:03.310 --> 19:05.590
the partners behind the scenes.

19:06.200 --> 19:06.830
Please leave.

19:06.830 --> 19:07.350
Sorry.

19:07.350 --> 19:08.000
Please leave.

19:08.000 --> 19:08.640
Sorry.

19:11.250 --> 19:12.310
I've checked the contracts.

19:12.310 --> 19:13.110
No problems.

19:16.310 --> 19:17.070
It's a pleasure working with you.

19:17.070 --> 19:17.750
Looking forward
to a pleasant collaboration.

19:17.750 --> 19:18.530
Looking forward
to a pleasant collaboration.

19:18.530 --> 19:20.200
[Luna Apparel Co., Ltd.]

19:20.680 --> 19:21.400
Alright.

19:22.000 --> 19:23.110
Okay. Bye.

19:23.510 --> 19:24.000
Chen.

19:24.590 --> 19:25.320
Look at this.

19:30.960 --> 19:32.090
The shop and fabrics

19:32.270 --> 19:33.110
are settled.

19:33.210 --> 19:34.520
The rest will be easy.

19:34.740 --> 19:36.070
For promotion and marketing,

19:36.070 --> 19:37.400
we'll just expand

19:37.400 --> 19:38.750
from our existing

19:38.830 --> 19:39.960
direct-sale stores.

19:39.960 --> 19:40.480
Okay.

19:40.960 --> 19:42.290
Let's call it a day then.

19:42.920 --> 19:45.510
After all,
there's something important to do.

19:45.510 --> 19:46.770
What important thing?

19:47.310 --> 19:48.070
You forgot?

19:48.480 --> 19:49.440
Didn't I arrange dinner

19:49.440 --> 19:51.200
with a businessman from Hushi last week?

19:51.200 --> 19:51.750
Did you?

19:52.510 --> 19:53.270
You forgot.

19:53.440 --> 19:55.100
We're running late. Let's go.

19:55.870 --> 19:57.430
Maybe I really did forget.

19:59.200 --> 20:00.160
What kind of business

20:00.160 --> 20:02.160
needs to be discussed
at Zhou Cheng and Kang Wei's place?

20:02.160 --> 20:03.490
Do you take me for a fool?

20:03.590 --> 20:04.400
I'd like to see

20:04.400 --> 20:05.550
what you're up to.

20:07.960 --> 20:10.640
Happy birthday!

20:12.440 --> 20:13.000
Xiaolan.

20:13.950 --> 20:14.880
Happy birthday.

20:19.240 --> 20:20.240
I actually forgot

20:21.110 --> 20:22.310
that today is

20:23.170 --> 20:24.830
this Xia Xiaolan's birthday.

20:24.830 --> 20:28.440
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

20:28.830 --> 20:30.480
I remember when I first came here,

20:28.860 --> 20:32.440
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

20:31.240 --> 20:32.920
this Xia Xiaolan had just celebrated

20:32.920 --> 20:34.070
her 18th birthday.

20:32.980 --> 20:36.620
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

20:35.580 --> 20:37.160
Now she's 25.

20:37.480 --> 20:41.160
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

20:38.070 --> 20:39.070
It's been so long.

20:41.270 --> 20:42.400
Blow out the candles

20:42.420 --> 20:43.160
and make a wish!

20:43.160 --> 20:43.820
Make a wish.

20:43.960 --> 20:45.290
Make a wish. Make a wish.

21:02.210 --> 21:02.970
Xia Xiaolan,

21:03.030 --> 21:03.960
happy birthday.

21:04.720 --> 21:05.480
Xia Xiaolan,

21:05.480 --> 21:06.440
happy birthday.

21:15.640 --> 21:16.230
Xia,

21:16.890 --> 21:18.020
make a wish for Luna.

21:19.030 --> 21:20.960
And our building materials store.

21:22.240 --> 21:23.000
You must keep the last wish

21:23.000 --> 21:23.830
for yourself.

21:28.030 --> 21:28.880
Xiaolan?

21:30.380 --> 21:32.240
Hurry up and blow out the candles.

21:33.590 --> 21:34.240
Xiaolan?

21:35.070 --> 21:35.870
What's wrong?

21:37.030 --> 21:37.590
Nothing.

21:38.000 --> 21:39.460
I'll blow out the candles.

21:47.680 --> 21:48.550
I made a wish

21:48.550 --> 21:49.590
for everyone here.

21:49.590 --> 21:51.790
I hope you all prosper.

21:52.070 --> 21:53.480
Xia is too selfless.

21:53.590 --> 21:55.110
She gave all her wishes to us.

21:55.110 --> 21:56.110
Now that you think about it,

21:56.110 --> 21:57.000
all of our

21:57.000 --> 21:57.640
businesses

21:57.640 --> 21:58.880
are in partnership with Xiaolan.

21:58.880 --> 22:00.000
So if our wishes come true,

22:00.000 --> 22:01.160
Xiaolan's will come true too.

22:01.160 --> 22:02.750
She really calculated that well.

22:02.750 --> 22:03.960
You're so smart, aren't you?

22:03.960 --> 22:04.590
Alright.

22:04.720 --> 22:05.790
Let's cut the cake.

22:05.880 --> 22:06.660
I'll go get the knife.

22:06.660 --> 22:07.550
Wait, wait!

22:10.790 --> 22:12.400
-Xia! Xia!
-Wei!

22:13.000 --> 22:13.900
Alright, that's enough.

22:13.900 --> 22:14.920
No more drinking.

22:14.920 --> 22:16.320
You can't drink anymore.

22:17.000 --> 22:17.860
I can handle it.

22:18.480 --> 22:19.750
I'm so full.

22:19.880 --> 22:21.940
You can't force the birthday girl
to drink like this.

22:21.940 --> 22:22.920
You won. He threw up.

22:22.920 --> 22:23.920
He threw up. He threw up.

22:23.920 --> 22:24.510
I'm really fine.

22:24.510 --> 22:25.030
Alright.

22:25.030 --> 22:25.510
Alright, alright.

22:25.510 --> 22:26.200
You know, in the past,

22:26.200 --> 22:26.750
when I went to business dinners,

22:26.750 --> 22:28.110
I drank way more than this.

22:28.110 --> 22:29.440
Besides, I have you.

22:31.550 --> 22:32.070
That is...

22:32.070 --> 22:33.270
Mr. Chen's fault.

22:33.350 --> 22:34.480
How could you take our Ms. Xia...

22:34.480 --> 22:35.110
to business dinners?

22:35.110 --> 22:36.240
What were you doing?

22:36.270 --> 22:37.270
I didn't.

22:37.420 --> 22:38.000
Alright.

22:38.270 --> 22:39.270
From now on, I‘ll protect

22:39.270 --> 22:39.930
my Xiaolan.

22:42.160 --> 22:43.130
What are you saying?

22:43.130 --> 22:45.210
What kind of talk is this?

22:47.960 --> 22:49.680
♪ Sometimes ♪

22:49.960 --> 22:51.400
♪ Sometimes ♪

22:51.920 --> 22:55.830
♪ I'd rather believe
everything has an end ♪

22:57.270 --> 22:58.350
This song isn't good.

22:58.350 --> 22:59.440
It's too depressing.

22:59.440 --> 23:00.440
What song is this?

23:00.480 --> 23:01.310
I haven't heard it.

23:01.310 --> 23:02.510
You haven't heard it?

23:06.680 --> 23:07.970
This song hasn't been released yet.

23:07.970 --> 23:08.880
I sang it too early.

23:08.880 --> 23:10.010
You'll know in time.

23:11.510 --> 23:12.110
Xiaolan,

23:12.510 --> 23:13.590
you've been saying some

23:13.590 --> 23:14.920
strange things lately.

23:15.070 --> 23:16.000
But you know,

23:16.750 --> 23:18.350
you're kind of cute this way.

23:19.240 --> 23:20.030
Do you know?

23:20.720 --> 23:21.880
When someone

23:22.790 --> 23:23.590
thinks a girl

23:23.590 --> 23:24.880
isn't that pretty,

23:24.880 --> 23:26.110
they call her cute.

23:26.310 --> 23:27.110
But I know

23:27.410 --> 23:29.170
you think I'm too pretty,

23:29.200 --> 23:30.660
so you call me cute, right?

23:32.400 --> 23:33.240
So when you are drunk,

23:33.240 --> 23:34.240
you are like this?

23:34.640 --> 23:36.040
Did I realize it too late?

23:36.920 --> 23:37.830
Yeah.

23:38.030 --> 23:39.510
I was a student before,

23:39.750 --> 23:40.790
so I couldn't drink.

23:40.790 --> 23:42.030
Drinking too much wasn't good.

23:42.030 --> 23:43.510
But it's different now.

23:44.440 --> 23:46.070
I'm an entrepreneur.

23:48.880 --> 23:49.960
Zhou Cheng,

23:50.400 --> 23:52.030
why are you so nice?

23:52.480 --> 23:53.960
Everything about you is great.

23:53.960 --> 23:56.160
You're handsome
and have a great personality.

23:56.160 --> 23:57.290
No matter what I say,

23:57.510 --> 23:58.440
you understand.

23:58.960 --> 24:00.750
And even if I don't say it,
you still understand.

24:00.750 --> 24:02.150
If you don't understand,

24:02.270 --> 24:04.400
you don't try to get to the bottom of it.

24:04.640 --> 24:05.680
You are simply...

24:05.680 --> 24:07.480
custom-made for me, aren't you?

24:08.000 --> 24:09.160
Could it be true

24:09.440 --> 24:11.480
that the game read my preferences?

24:11.680 --> 24:13.200
Seeing that
I've been single for so many years,

24:13.200 --> 24:14.270
it felt sorry for me

24:14.510 --> 24:15.830
and custom-made

24:15.830 --> 24:16.750
a lover for me.

24:19.000 --> 24:21.160
Your model looks really good.

24:22.640 --> 24:23.350
However,

24:23.760 --> 24:24.970
if I leave here,

24:25.000 --> 24:26.460
will I never see you again?

24:28.440 --> 24:30.300
Then I really don't want to leave.

24:33.590 --> 24:34.160
Xiaolan.

24:35.640 --> 24:36.970
No matter what happens,

24:37.310 --> 24:38.840
and no matter where you are,

24:39.480 --> 24:40.550
I will be with you.

24:51.830 --> 24:53.550
The place I'm going to in the future,

24:53.550 --> 24:55.010
you might not be able to go.

24:55.350 --> 24:56.480
As for the future...

24:57.000 --> 24:58.750
we can talk about it in the future.

24:58.750 --> 24:59.640
Right now,

25:00.640 --> 25:02.170
let's go where we need to go.

25:05.830 --> 25:06.760
I don't think...

25:07.510 --> 25:08.570
this is a good idea.

25:09.170 --> 25:10.410
I think it's fine.

26:03.070 --> 26:05.030
I feel like
I've forgotten something important.

26:05.030 --> 26:06.820
Xia Xiaolan, happy birthday.

26:07.240 --> 26:08.070
Xia Xiaolan,

26:08.070 --> 26:09.000
happy birthday.

26:09.160 --> 26:10.090
Happy birthday.

26:12.070 --> 26:12.750
Birthday?

26:14.240 --> 26:15.970
I forgot my original birthday.

26:20.440 --> 26:22.040
Even this pen has gotten old.

26:22.720 --> 26:24.250
I've been here for too long.

26:24.880 --> 26:26.680
Long enough that I've forgotten

26:26.890 --> 26:28.450
my original self.

26:31.640 --> 26:32.510
This day

26:31.950 --> 26:33.140
[New Year's Day, 2026, Xia household]

26:33.070 --> 26:34.270
is where it all began.

26:35.000 --> 26:35.790
I will write down

26:35.790 --> 26:37.000
all the days

26:37.030 --> 26:38.160
worth remembering.

26:38.520 --> 26:39.160
I can't

26:39.160 --> 26:40.400
forget my true self.

26:42.830 --> 26:43.880
1998.

26:44.790 --> 26:46.880
My first trip with Mom and Dad.

26:47.720 --> 26:49.050
The destination was...

26:52.640 --> 26:54.770
We got in a car accident on the way back.

26:55.480 --> 26:57.210
That's not worth remembering.

27:05.350 --> 27:07.480
Luna will go bankrupt in a few months.

27:07.920 --> 27:08.780
It's a bad omen.

27:08.920 --> 27:09.520
Forget it.

27:35.750 --> 27:37.080
It turns out my past self

27:37.500 --> 27:39.300
had nothing worth remembering.

27:40.400 --> 27:42.000
But every day of the present,

27:42.270 --> 27:43.550
I don't want to forget.

27:45.000 --> 27:45.880
If possible,

27:47.110 --> 27:48.570
I want to stay here forever

27:49.200 --> 27:50.930
and become the new Xia Xiaolan.

27:53.220 --> 27:54.030
From the moment I met

27:54.030 --> 27:55.680
Chen Xiliang,

27:56.480 --> 27:58.480
the gears of fate began to turn.

27:59.790 --> 28:01.680
Are those forgotten memories

28:04.080 --> 28:05.920
a countdown to my departure?

28:15.350 --> 28:15.960
Mom.

28:20.200 --> 28:20.880
Xiaolan.

28:21.880 --> 28:22.480
Come here.

28:23.270 --> 28:24.730
You had a nightmare again?

28:28.550 --> 28:29.480
Don't be afraid.

28:29.920 --> 28:30.720
Mom is here.

28:32.820 --> 28:34.100
Stroke your hair;

28:34.480 --> 28:35.880
there's nothing to fear.

28:37.750 --> 28:38.480
Go to sleep.

28:44.510 --> 28:46.440
I used to worry that without me,

28:46.790 --> 28:48.390
she couldn't live on her own.

28:49.310 --> 28:50.640
But now it seems

28:51.680 --> 28:53.340
I'm the one who needs her more.

28:54.070 --> 28:55.470
I can't leave this place.

28:55.960 --> 28:57.290
I can't leave everyone.

29:12.680 --> 29:13.620
Why are you here?

29:13.750 --> 29:14.750
To take me to work?

29:14.970 --> 29:17.200
I came to see if my comrade
who got drunk yesterday

29:17.200 --> 29:18.060
has a headache.

29:18.110 --> 29:19.310
Do you need an escort?

29:19.350 --> 29:19.830
Well...

29:20.160 --> 29:21.490
what about the law firm?

29:21.830 --> 29:22.790
After all, I'm a lawyer

29:22.790 --> 29:24.050
handling my own cases now.

29:24.050 --> 29:25.180
I have some freedom.

29:26.320 --> 29:28.210
Attorney Zhou is so impressive.

29:28.240 --> 29:29.700
Impressive and handsome.

29:30.070 --> 29:30.830
Of course.

29:31.670 --> 29:33.520
I can't let a certain someone,

29:33.550 --> 29:34.510
when she's drunk,

29:34.510 --> 29:36.180
cling to me, crying and fussing,

29:36.180 --> 29:37.240
refusing to let go,

29:37.310 --> 29:38.370
saying things like

29:38.440 --> 29:39.320
she doesn't want to go back

29:39.320 --> 29:40.350
and that if she does,

29:40.350 --> 29:41.880
her boyfriend will be gone.

29:42.720 --> 29:43.780
What else did I say?

29:45.160 --> 29:45.680
Why?

29:46.110 --> 29:47.970
Afraid that you spilled a secret?

29:49.310 --> 29:50.570
I'm not afraid of that.

29:50.640 --> 29:51.750
Because even if I said it,

29:51.750 --> 29:53.110
you probably wouldn't believe it.

29:53.110 --> 29:53.840
Don't worry.

29:54.110 --> 29:55.240
You didn't say much.

29:55.310 --> 29:56.570
You just did a lot of...

29:56.790 --> 29:58.120
inappropriate things.

30:00.510 --> 30:02.270
I think I remembered some of it.

30:02.550 --> 30:03.160
You did?

30:03.160 --> 30:03.880
But...

30:04.110 --> 30:04.720
You need a reminder?

30:04.720 --> 30:05.270
No, no, no.

30:05.270 --> 30:06.880
It doesn't matter if I can't remember.

30:06.880 --> 30:07.480
First...

30:07.480 --> 30:08.200
Stop that.

30:08.350 --> 30:09.550
-And then...
-It's okay.

30:09.550 --> 30:10.010
Really.

30:10.020 --> 30:10.630
Xiaolan.

30:11.270 --> 30:12.000
I'm here to pick up the suit.

30:12.000 --> 30:12.730
You're here.

30:12.960 --> 30:14.360
Okay, I'll get it for you.

30:22.160 --> 30:23.510
This dress is beautiful.

30:23.510 --> 30:24.960
Yes, I like it.

30:26.030 --> 30:27.290
Can you come over here?

30:29.920 --> 30:30.960
Can you tell me

30:30.960 --> 30:32.590
about this dress? Thank you.

30:33.070 --> 30:34.310
No, no, no.

30:34.330 --> 30:35.960
I... don't understand.

30:36.070 --> 30:37.550
I... I don't work here.

30:37.630 --> 30:38.700
Hello, ladies.

30:38.730 --> 30:39.810
How can I help you?

30:39.960 --> 30:41.000
What would you like?

30:41.000 --> 30:43.160
We are looking for some dresses.

30:43.350 --> 30:43.960
Dress?

30:44.000 --> 30:44.440
Yeah.

30:44.440 --> 30:44.960
Okay.

30:45.110 --> 30:46.510
The dresses are over there.

30:46.510 --> 30:48.790
This is a Chinese-style dress.

30:49.200 --> 30:52.550
The flower is...
Chinese traditional culture.

30:52.590 --> 30:54.000
It's beautiful, but...

30:54.030 --> 30:55.960
There are more dresses over there.

30:55.960 --> 30:57.030
Please follow me.

30:58.880 --> 31:01.480
This is a black and white dress.

31:01.690 --> 31:02.960
Please let me know

31:02.960 --> 31:04.110
if you need any help.

31:04.680 --> 31:05.680
Okay, okay.

31:07.030 --> 31:08.430
Are blonde women pretty?

31:10.010 --> 31:10.520
Well...

31:10.550 --> 31:11.550
I mean... that...

31:11.750 --> 31:13.680
You Li's English is so amazing now?

31:13.880 --> 31:14.480
Yeah.

31:14.480 --> 31:15.400
Our You is now

31:15.420 --> 31:16.970
a completely different person.

31:16.970 --> 31:18.200
She speaks a bit of English and Cantonese.

31:18.200 --> 31:20.000
Handling customers is no problem at all.

31:20.000 --> 31:20.830
How about I come

31:20.830 --> 31:21.680
and work in your shop?

31:21.680 --> 31:22.740
It's such good training.

31:22.740 --> 31:23.780
Give me a break.

31:24.030 --> 31:25.480
Shengcheng is full of people

31:25.480 --> 31:26.400
speaking English and Cantonese.

31:26.400 --> 31:27.480
Why come here?

31:28.240 --> 31:29.170
I'm telling you,

31:29.310 --> 31:30.350
if you don't improve yourself,

31:30.350 --> 31:31.720
you won't even be able
to do business later.

31:31.720 --> 31:32.720
Got it, got it.

31:33.200 --> 31:33.730
Alright.

31:33.960 --> 31:34.750
Chen Xiliang

31:34.750 --> 31:35.880
picked this out especially for you.

31:35.880 --> 31:38.080
You need to dress well to talk business.

31:38.440 --> 31:39.240
I'll try it on.

31:39.400 --> 31:39.930
Go ahead.

31:40.030 --> 31:40.880
Okay.

31:45.440 --> 31:46.510
What's the progress

31:46.510 --> 31:47.400
on this case?

31:47.690 --> 31:48.830
The client now believes

31:48.830 --> 31:49.440
that this shop

31:49.440 --> 31:51.310
was funded and run by him from the start,

31:51.310 --> 31:52.750
with the other party just helping out.

31:52.750 --> 31:54.280
So, it's not a partnership.

31:55.370 --> 31:56.000
So now he

31:56.030 --> 31:57.550
only wants to pay the other party
a basic salary.

31:57.550 --> 31:58.070
Chen.

31:58.650 --> 31:59.720
You have the qualification certificate

31:59.720 --> 32:00.880
of the company in Hangcheng, right?

32:00.880 --> 32:01.270
Yes.

32:01.440 --> 32:02.440
Wait a moment.

32:06.000 --> 32:06.400
Here.

32:07.030 --> 32:07.490
Thanks.

32:10.780 --> 32:11.840
The plaintiff says

32:11.880 --> 32:13.750
this is the maximum he can accept.

32:13.960 --> 32:16.090
Both sides are in a deadlock right now.

32:17.110 --> 32:18.550
The other party's stance is

32:18.550 --> 32:20.310
that it must be calculated
as a partnership.

32:20.310 --> 32:21.880
If they don't pay, they'll sue, right?

32:21.880 --> 32:22.310
Yes.

32:22.960 --> 32:25.270
So it's hard to make progress.

32:26.840 --> 32:28.770
Since we represent the plaintiff,

32:28.920 --> 32:31.720
let's proceed
with the current litigation terms.

32:33.340 --> 32:37.290
[Luna]

32:34.000 --> 32:34.590
Bye-bye.

32:57.040 --> 32:58.200
Who are you? Let go of me!

32:58.200 --> 33:00.060
-What are you doing?
-Who are you?

33:01.160 --> 33:01.820
Don't move!

33:04.830 --> 33:05.750
Xia Hongxia?

33:09.000 --> 33:09.680
You did it?

33:10.070 --> 33:10.800
Yes, I did it.

33:10.890 --> 33:11.520
So what?

33:12.720 --> 33:13.240
You...

33:13.730 --> 33:14.390
Don't move!

33:14.920 --> 33:15.550
Zhou Cheng,

33:15.550 --> 33:16.270
let her go.

33:33.510 --> 33:34.680
There's candy too?

33:40.920 --> 33:41.750
What are you looking at?

33:41.750 --> 33:43.550
Your shop was exactly my target.

33:43.930 --> 33:44.790
It serves you right for being unfilial.

33:44.790 --> 33:46.050
You have such a big shop

33:46.070 --> 33:46.880
and so much money,

33:46.880 --> 33:48.070
but you won't support my second uncle

33:48.070 --> 33:49.070
and grandma.

33:49.270 --> 33:50.070
You know what?

33:50.270 --> 33:51.510
Uncle Dajun has been kicked out

33:51.510 --> 33:52.970
by that boss from Gangdao.

33:55.350 --> 33:56.640
It seems your family

33:56.680 --> 33:58.880
came to Shengcheng to rely on Xia Dajun.

33:59.240 --> 34:00.680
If he chooses to be a fool

34:00.680 --> 34:01.880
and support parasites like you,

34:01.880 --> 34:02.960
it's none of my business.

34:02.960 --> 34:03.550
But if you

34:03.550 --> 34:04.880
come to my shop to cause trouble again,

34:04.880 --> 34:06.610
I won't let you get away with it.

34:07.200 --> 34:08.110
Anyway, right now,

34:08.110 --> 34:09.300
we can't even survive.

34:09.300 --> 34:11.429
Just give me some money and I'll leave.

34:12.920 --> 34:13.800
Your surname is Xia.

34:13.800 --> 34:15.510
You can't ignore your family.

34:15.590 --> 34:17.120
Why should I care about you?

34:17.480 --> 34:19.000
When you wanted me dead back then,

34:19.000 --> 34:20.199
no one cared about me.

34:24.190 --> 34:25.070
Attorney Zhou,

34:25.440 --> 34:26.510
teach her some law.

34:27.110 --> 34:29.150
For someone like her who smashes windows,

34:29.150 --> 34:29.840
breaks into a shop,

34:29.840 --> 34:30.840
and steals food,

34:31.320 --> 34:32.800
what's the usual sentence?

34:32.800 --> 34:34.000
Three years minimum.

34:34.550 --> 34:35.679
Five years maximum.

34:36.400 --> 34:38.260
For a situation like yours today,

34:38.670 --> 34:40.400
a case can definitely be filed.

34:40.510 --> 34:41.000
I...

34:41.190 --> 34:43.190
I'd like to see who dares to arrest me.

34:43.190 --> 34:45.280
I... I'm a Xia too.

34:45.400 --> 34:46.030
Your things

34:46.030 --> 34:47.320
all belong to the Xia family.

34:47.320 --> 34:48.230
So what if I smashed them?

34:48.230 --> 34:49.070
What can you do to me?

34:49.070 --> 34:49.929
What can you do?

34:52.110 --> 34:53.030
Xia Hongxia,

34:53.630 --> 34:54.880
did you get your head

34:54.880 --> 34:56.210
caught in a door before?

34:56.550 --> 34:58.080
Turn around and take a look.

34:58.230 --> 34:59.670
Of that whole Xia family,

34:59.880 --> 35:01.840
is there anyone
who actually cares about you

35:01.840 --> 35:03.510
or considers your well-being?

35:03.510 --> 35:04.400
That old woman

35:04.400 --> 35:05.630
sent you here today, didn't she?

35:05.630 --> 35:06.800
Since it's illegal,

35:06.880 --> 35:08.400
why didn't she come herself?

35:08.400 --> 35:09.510
Why didn't she ask Xia Junbao

35:09.510 --> 35:10.230
or Xia Junshan to come

35:10.230 --> 35:11.090
instead of you?

35:12.480 --> 35:13.920
You're in your 20s.

35:14.230 --> 35:16.160
Why is your head still full of mush?

35:17.160 --> 35:18.190
Xia Xiaolan, you...

35:18.190 --> 35:20.670
You have a sharp tongue.
I can't out-talk you.

35:20.670 --> 35:21.880
But I won't listen to you anyway.

35:21.880 --> 35:23.070
You're just a jinx!

35:23.150 --> 35:23.960
If we can't live well,

35:23.960 --> 35:25.000
neither can you!

35:25.190 --> 35:25.880
Believe it or not,

35:25.880 --> 35:27.280
I'll smash this shop!

35:27.760 --> 35:28.290
Smash it.

35:31.190 --> 35:32.250
What are you doing?

35:33.180 --> 35:33.740
Do it.

35:33.920 --> 35:34.650
Do it and see.

35:39.200 --> 35:39.920
I gave you a chance,

35:39.920 --> 35:41.050
but you're useless.

35:43.630 --> 35:44.480
Xia Hongxia,

35:44.710 --> 35:45.570
let me tell you.

35:45.840 --> 35:46.920
Money doesn't

35:46.920 --> 35:48.110
grow on trees.

35:48.360 --> 35:49.620
It's all hard-earned.

35:50.080 --> 35:51.110
Do you know why your Xia family

35:51.110 --> 35:52.070
is so poor,

35:52.440 --> 35:54.570
poor from Dahe Village to Shengcheng?

35:54.590 --> 35:55.110
It's because

35:55.110 --> 35:56.970
you always want to rely on others.

35:57.280 --> 35:58.230
Everything I have now,

35:58.230 --> 35:59.670
I earned myself.

35:59.960 --> 36:00.820
You want money?

36:00.880 --> 36:02.480
There are opportunities
everywhere in Shengcheng.

36:02.480 --> 36:03.610
Go earn it yourself.

36:04.190 --> 36:04.840
I...

36:05.400 --> 36:06.930
Since you're already here,

36:07.030 --> 36:07.800
I'd feel bad

36:07.800 --> 36:09.730
letting you go back empty-handed.

36:10.000 --> 36:11.510
There are some cardboard boxes
in the warehouse back there.

36:11.510 --> 36:12.840
Take them and sell them.

36:15.630 --> 36:16.360
You...

36:17.710 --> 36:18.910
You're insulting me!

36:20.960 --> 36:23.020
Remember to pay me back for the glass!

36:25.800 --> 36:26.670
So this is that cousin

36:26.670 --> 36:28.230
from your third uncle's family?

36:28.230 --> 36:29.960
She really hasn't changed a bit.

36:29.960 --> 36:30.960
What do you think of her?

36:30.960 --> 36:32.030
Did you fall in love?

36:32.030 --> 36:33.070
She's young and energetic,

36:33.070 --> 36:34.600
and good at smashing glass.

36:38.710 --> 36:40.000
I actually think

36:40.070 --> 36:41.590
Xia Hongxia isn't bad.

36:41.960 --> 36:43.030
She's just too poor,

36:43.030 --> 36:45.030
and no one taught her the right path.

36:46.440 --> 36:47.840
That's why I wasn't

36:47.840 --> 36:48.800
just scaring her.

36:48.800 --> 36:50.280
I wanted to talk some sense into her.

36:50.280 --> 36:52.280
I hope she can figure it out herself.

36:53.760 --> 36:54.560
Fortunately,

36:54.670 --> 36:55.840
I escaped that pit

36:55.840 --> 36:57.300
of the Xia family long ago.

36:59.120 --> 37:00.070
I don't think Xia Hongxia

37:00.070 --> 37:01.290
is stupid enough to

37:01.330 --> 37:02.160
just pass by,

37:02.190 --> 37:03.150
see you, and decide to come over

37:03.150 --> 37:04.280
and smash the glass.

37:04.450 --> 37:05.230
She must have known long ago

37:05.230 --> 37:06.430
that it was your shop.

37:06.920 --> 37:07.780
How do you think

37:07.960 --> 37:08.880
she knew?

37:10.000 --> 37:11.710
Who else could be connected

37:11.710 --> 37:12.710
to the Xia family?

37:12.800 --> 37:14.460
That Young Master, of course.

37:27.440 --> 37:29.000
So you saw her?

37:29.070 --> 37:29.760
No!

37:30.030 --> 37:31.230
No?

37:31.930 --> 37:33.770
If you didn't see her,

37:33.800 --> 37:35.030
who else

37:35.030 --> 37:36.070
could have made our Hongxia

37:36.070 --> 37:37.760
so angry?

37:38.550 --> 37:39.150
Grandma,

37:39.440 --> 37:40.550
so you know Xia Xiaolan

37:40.550 --> 37:41.510
can make people angry?

37:41.510 --> 37:43.030
Then why did you send me?

37:43.110 --> 37:43.710
Why didn't you send

37:43.710 --> 37:44.590
your two grandsons?

37:44.590 --> 37:45.520
-I...
-Hongxia!

37:46.920 --> 37:48.230
How can you talk to Grandma like that?

37:48.230 --> 37:49.400
So what if I do?

37:49.480 --> 37:50.190
Grandma,

37:50.400 --> 37:51.400
you're a woman too.

37:51.400 --> 37:53.000
Why do you only pick on women?

37:53.000 --> 37:53.800
When you were home,

37:53.800 --> 37:54.670
you bullied my second aunt.

37:54.670 --> 37:55.320
Now that we're out,

37:55.320 --> 37:56.150
you bully me.

37:56.150 --> 37:56.630
You...

37:56.630 --> 37:58.320
What nonsense are you talking about?

37:58.320 --> 37:59.850
What are you talking about?

37:59.850 --> 38:01.110
-Mother...
-Get lost!

38:01.590 --> 38:02.030
Come on.

38:02.030 --> 38:02.510
Mother, don't...

38:02.510 --> 38:03.040
Get lost!

38:06.230 --> 38:07.510
I knew that

38:07.510 --> 38:08.550
Xia Xiaolan's money

38:08.550 --> 38:09.800
would be hard to get.

38:10.230 --> 38:11.800
But aren't you capable?

38:11.980 --> 38:13.280
Aren't you full of tricks?

38:13.280 --> 38:15.070
Are you able to get it?

38:16.920 --> 38:17.760
What are you acting

38:17.760 --> 38:20.280
so high and mighty
for now that you're home?

38:20.620 --> 38:22.760
Did you get the money or not?

38:22.760 --> 38:23.840
Did you pocket it?

38:24.960 --> 38:26.840
She gave me a pile of scrap cardboard

38:26.840 --> 38:28.440
and told me to earn it myself!

38:28.440 --> 38:29.730
You... I...

38:29.760 --> 38:30.440
Hongxia!

38:31.440 --> 38:32.110
Hongxia!

38:34.150 --> 38:35.630
Dajun!

38:36.000 --> 38:37.440
Look at the precious daughter

38:37.440 --> 38:39.280
you raised!

38:39.640 --> 38:42.080
She's rotten to the core!

38:42.110 --> 38:43.760
Xia Dajun!

38:45.150 --> 38:46.440
How many times have I told you

38:46.440 --> 38:47.360
not to provoke her?

38:47.360 --> 38:48.590
I told you not to ask for money,

38:48.590 --> 38:50.230
but no one listened!

38:54.550 --> 38:57.760
Now you've got an attitude?

39:04.780 --> 39:07.280
[Happy Life Materials Center]

39:32.460 --> 39:36.240
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

39:37.590 --> 39:39.910
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

39:40.830 --> 39:43.120
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

39:45.690 --> 39:49.890
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

39:50.790 --> 39:53.300
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

39:53.320 --> 39:57.070
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

39:57.630 --> 40:00.030
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

40:01.270 --> 40:03.810
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

40:04.590 --> 40:07.190
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

40:05.960 --> 40:07.230
You are currently at

40:07.230 --> 40:08.400
the furniture section.

40:07.830 --> 40:12.320
♪ Our youth ♪

40:08.440 --> 40:10.070
There is
a building materials section ahead.

40:10.070 --> 40:11.550
Write down the item numbers
of what you like,

40:11.550 --> 40:12.590
and pay at the front.

40:12.590 --> 40:13.280
If you're interested,

40:12.810 --> 40:16.180
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

40:13.280 --> 40:14.880
I can take you to the showroom
to see how it looks.

40:14.880 --> 40:16.710
Our lighting selection here

40:16.210 --> 40:19.640
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

40:16.840 --> 40:17.760
is the most complete.

40:17.760 --> 40:19.030
Because when we were at Renmin Bridge,

40:19.030 --> 40:19.860
we specialized in lights.

40:19.860 --> 40:22.630
♪ We never give up ♪

40:20.030 --> 40:21.030
Our lighting selection here

40:21.030 --> 40:22.280
is arguably the most complete

40:22.280 --> 40:23.510
and best in Shengcheng.

40:23.250 --> 40:26.620
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

40:23.630 --> 40:24.550
The biggest feature here

40:24.550 --> 40:25.960
is our

40:26.000 --> 40:26.960
one-stop service—

40:26.640 --> 40:29.800
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

40:27.230 --> 40:28.320
hard furnishings, soft furnishings—

40:28.320 --> 40:29.820
everything can be done here at once.

40:29.820 --> 40:33.180
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

40:31.670 --> 40:33.480
98, 99—10,000.

40:33.370 --> 40:36.280
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

40:36.720 --> 40:39.880
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

40:40.100 --> 40:45.770
♪ That'd be enough ♪

40:45.000 --> 40:46.070
We have so many orders

40:46.070 --> 40:47.400
on our first day!

40:47.960 --> 40:49.090
This is the deposit.

40:49.230 --> 40:50.150
And retail sales.

40:50.150 --> 40:52.000
Xiaolan's side handles pre-sales.

40:52.000 --> 40:52.670
Xiaolan,

40:53.000 --> 40:53.920
how is the building materials business

40:53.920 --> 40:55.320
doing so well?

40:56.030 --> 40:56.760
Yeah.

40:56.840 --> 40:59.000
The smell of money is good.

40:59.670 --> 41:00.880
Because you guys have already

41:00.880 --> 41:02.880
been in the building materials business
for a while.

41:02.880 --> 41:04.280
From supply to sales,

41:04.320 --> 41:05.440
everything is established.

41:05.440 --> 41:06.360
Now we are just

41:06.360 --> 41:07.510
expanding the scale

41:07.510 --> 41:08.920
and running operations holistically.

41:08.920 --> 41:09.880
Today's sales

41:09.880 --> 41:11.340
are about what I expected.

41:11.840 --> 41:12.360
See?

41:12.360 --> 41:13.320
Listening to Xiaolan

41:13.320 --> 41:14.630
is never wrong.

41:14.760 --> 41:15.760
Great. Great.

41:16.190 --> 41:17.150
Don't just sit there.

41:17.150 --> 41:17.710
Help me count.

41:17.710 --> 41:18.510
I'll count.

41:20.840 --> 41:21.760
So much money?

41:22.450 --> 41:24.200
Did you rob a bank?

41:24.920 --> 41:25.760
What do you say?

41:25.760 --> 41:27.110
Want some?

41:27.110 --> 41:28.440
I earned quite a lot too.

41:30.010 --> 41:30.560
So,

41:30.590 --> 41:31.800
how far are you

41:31.800 --> 41:33.130
from your savings goal?

41:33.670 --> 41:35.800
If things go well with Luna,

41:36.280 --> 41:37.280
it should be soon.

41:38.990 --> 41:40.280
If you're free, help me count

41:40.280 --> 41:41.070
how much money is here.
